%%{init: {'theme':'neutral', 'themeVariables': {'fontSize':'13px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant S as BookMyShowService
    participant L as SeatLockProvider
    participant Sh as Show
    participant P as PricingStrategy
    participant Pay as PaymentStrategy
    participant O as Observers

    Note over User,O: Phase 1 — HOLD (temporary, all-or-nothing)
    User->>S: holdSeats(show, [A1,A2], alice)
    S->>Sh: showSeat(id).isBooked()?  (fast fail)
    S->>L: lockSeats(show, [A1,A2], alice, ttl)
    Note right of L: per seat: compute(key) installs a<br/>SeatLock iff free/expired — ATOMIC.<br/>any conflict → rollback all → throw
    L-->>S: ok
    S->>Sh: re-check isBooked() (closes TOCTOU)
    S->>O: onSeatsHeld(...)
    S-->>User: LockToken(expiresAt)

    Note over User,O: Phase 2 — CONFIRM (validate → pay → finalize)
    User->>S: confirmBooking(token, payment)
    S->>L: isValidLock(seats, alice)?  &  token not expired
    alt hold lapsed / not owned
        L-->>S: false
        S-->>User: throw InvalidLockException
    else still holds a live lock
        L-->>S: true
        S->>P: priceFor(show, seats)
        P-->>S: amount
        S->>Pay: pay(amount)
        alt declined
            Pay-->>S: declined
            S->>L: unlockSeats(seats, alice)
            S-->>User: throw PaymentFailedException
        else approved
            Pay-->>S: ok(txnId)
            S->>Sh: markBooked(A1,A2)  (durable, still holding lock)
            S->>L: unlockSeats(seats, alice)
            S->>O: onBookingConfirmed(booking)
            S-->>User: Booking(CONFIRMED)
        end
    end
